title: Spd Chancellorship
subtitle: Someone ought to be Chancellor candidate.
card-image: img/flags.jpg
tags: party_aff

= SPD Chancellor Candidate Selection

The SPD is the largest party in the coalition. Before presenting candidates to our coalition partners, we must decide which SPD figure to put forward as our preferred chancellor candidate.

**Available SPD Chancellor Candidates:**

[? if not muller_dead : **Hermann Müller** - Potential chancellor, experienced in coalition management, moderate reformist, respected across party lines. ?]

**Otto Wels** - Party Chairman since 1919, staunch republican, strong anti-Nazi credentials, represents party orthodoxy.

**Otto Braun** - Minister-President of Prussia, executive experience, pragmatic administrator, controls largest state government.

[? if spd_toleration = 0 : **Rudolf Hilferding** - Leading Marxist economist, intellectual heavyweight, appeals to left wing, controversial with bourgeois parties. ?]

**Who should the SPD put forward?**

- @prefer_mueller: Hermann Müller - Experience and moderation
- @prefer_wels: Otto Wels - Party unity and legitimacy
- @prefer_braun: Otto Braun - Executive competence
- @prefer_hilferding: Rudolf Hilferding - Left credibility
- @prefer_breitscheid: Breitscheid - International expet

@prefer_mueller
view-if: not muller_dead
on-arrival: {!
Q.spd_chancellor_preference = "mueller";
// Boost Müller's weight in candidate list
for (var i = 0; i < Q.chancellor_candidates.length; i++) {
    if (Q.chancellor_candidates[i].name === "Müller") {
        Q.chancellor_candidates[i].weight = 120;
        Q.chancellor_candidates[i].score = Q.chancellor_candidates[i].votes * 1.2;
    }
}
// Re-sort
Q.chancellor_candidates.sort(function(a, b) { return b.score - a.score; });
!}

Müller's experience and moderate reputation make him a strong choice for coalition building.

@prefer_wels
on-arrival: {!
Q.spd_chancellor_preference = "wels";
for (var i = 0; i < Q.chancellor_candidates.length; i++) {
    if (Q.chancellor_candidates[i].name === "Wels") {
        Q.chancellor_candidates[i].weight = 120;
        Q.chancellor_candidates[i].score = Q.chancellor_candidates[i].votes * 1.2;
    }
}
Q.chancellor_candidates.sort(function(a, b) { return b.score - a.score; });
!}

Wels as party chairman brings legitimacy and unity to our coalition offer.

