Braun's proven administrative record in Prussia demonstrates he can lead effectively.

@prefer_hilferding
view-if: spd_toleration = 0
on-arrival: {!
Q.spd_chancellor_preference = "hilferding";
for (var i = 0; i < Q.chancellor_candidates.length; i++) {
    if (Q.chancellor_candidates[i].name === "Hilferding") {
